How to run it manually in the terminal:
You will need three terminal windows open at the same time. Run these commands:

Terminal 1: Backend Service (Port 3002)

bash:
cd backend
npm install
npm start

Terminal 2: Frontend Landing Page (Port 3000)

bash:
cd frontend
npm install
npm start

Terminal 3: Trading Dashboard Portal (Port 3001)

bash:
cd dashboard
npm install
npm start
